959
01:22:43,734 --> 01:22:45,034
<i>Mereka semua sudah mati.</i>

960
01:22:45,035 --> 01:22:46,903
<i>Standish. Cavanaugh.</i>

961
01:22:46,904 --> 01:22:48,634
