yang datang.

1027
01:30:11,808 --> 01:30:14,100
Mereka butuh bantuan.

1028
01:30:14,101 --> 01:30:17,437
Pak, minta izin untuk mendarat.

1029
01:30:17,438 --> 01:30:19,022
<i>Negatif!</i>

1030
01:30:19,023 --> 01:30:21,483
<i>Jangan daratkan pesawat itu
di lautan luas!</i>

1031
01:30:21,484 --> 01:30:23,504
Jangan ambil resiko.

1032
01:30:25,446 --> 01:30:27,280
Aku akan mendarat.

1033
01:30:27,281 --> 01:30:29,331
Daratkan pesawat itu, Letnan.

1034
01:30:29,332 --> 01:30:30,925
Pegangan!

1035
01:30:42,797 --> 01:30:46,133
Astaga, mereka mendarat di air.

1036
01:30:46,134 --> 01:30:49,094
Bahan bakar kita hampir habis, pak.
Kita harus pergi.

1037
01:30:49,095 --> 01:30:50,945
<i>10-4, kembali ke markas.</i>

1038
01:30:53,182 --> 01:30:58,353
Dia melihat kita!

1039
01:32:47,463 --> 01:32:49,273
<i>Mendarat di laut!</i>

1040
01:32:52,135 --> 01:32:53,435
Astaga.

1041
01:32:59,267 --> 01:33:01,643
Bawa yang sendirian dulu./
Letnan...

1042
01:33:01,644 --> 01:33:03,154
...bukankah lebih cepat
membawa yang berkelompok?

1043
01:33:03,155 --> 01:33:04,980
Memang lebih cepat...

1044
01:33:04,981 --> 01:33:06,982
...tapi peluang bertahan
hidup mereka lebih besar.

1045
01:33:06,983 --> 01:33:09,985
Hei, nak, siapa namamu?
Apa yang terjadi di sini?

1046
01:33:09,986 --> 01:33:12,320
Brian Smithwick.

1047
01:33:12,321 --> 01:33:17,591
Pengirim Sinyal Kelas 1
di USS Indianapolis.

1048
01:33:19,245 --> 01:33:20,537
<i>Seimbangkan!
Lurus!</i>

1049
01:33:20,538 --> 01:33:22,289
Letnan, ruangnya tak cukup.

1050
01:33:22,290 --> 01:33:23,999
Naikkan lagi ke sayap.
Jangan lupa di bagian ekor.

1051
01:33:24,000 --> 01:33:26,585
Kita bisa taruh mereka di sana.
Perhatikan cleat-nya!

1052
01:33:26,586 --> 01:33:28,003
Kita akan pulang!

1053
01:33:28,004 --> 01:33:29,254
Apa kau serius...

1054
01:33:32,091 --> 01:33:34,426
Hei, tunggu!

1055
01:33:34,427 --> 01:33:36,052
Dia kapten kami.

1056
01:33:36,053 --> 01:33:38,073
Terima kasih...

1057
01:33:40,266 --> 01:33:43,018
