01:34:38,574 --> 01:34:42,118
<i>"Aku tak mengerti
mengapa lama sekali."</i>

1077
01:34:42,119 --> 01:34:45,330
<i>"Namun akhirnya lega juga."</i>

1078
01:34:45,331 --> 01:34:47,582
<i>Tak cukup ruang
di pesawat itu...</i>

1079
01:34:47,583 --> 01:34:52,587
<i>...untuk semua korban selamat,
namun kapal lain berdatangan."</i>

1080
01:34:52,588 --> 01:34:56,007
<i>Bassett, Ringness, Talbot...</i>

1081
01:34:56,008 --> 01:34:58,468
<i>...Register, Dulfilho...</i>

1082
01:34:58,469 --> 01:35:00,359
<i>...dan Cecil J. Doyle."</i>

1083
01:35:13,442 --> 01:35:16,611
Inilah yang kuinginkan.

1084
01:35:16,612 --> 01:35:19,281
Kapal pahlawan kita yang
mengantar bom sesuai jadwal..

1085
01:35:19,282 --> 01:35:21,741
